Package: CI.RCT.Sim
Title: Package to Facilitate a Simulation Study on Causal Inference Methods in RCTs
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    c(person("Tobias", "Fellinger", email="tobias.fellinger@ages.at", role=c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9474-2731")))
Description: This package includes the reusable functions, methods, ... for the simulation study on causal inference methods in randomized controlled trials as part of the EMA-tender research project conducted by the CONFIRMS consortium.
